company_name: MAPLASTIC GMBH TECHNISCHE UND MEDIZINISCHE KUNSTSTOFFPRODUKTE
information: The company MAPLASTIC GMBH TECHNISCHE UND MEDIZINISCHE KUNSTSTOFFPRODUKTE, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1969, which operates in the ORGANIC FARMING industry. It also operates in the Pets industries. It is based in Spangenberg, Germany.
